title: 3 BR House for Rent - Bright and Charming!
posting_body: ['Available Immediately.', 'Call', 'show contact info', 'for a private showing.', '1625 Oregon Avenue South, St. Louis Park, MN', 'Welcome to this wonderful home!', 'Great neighborhood close to parks, schools, and shopping.', 'There is quick access to the freeway system and downtown, yet tucked away on a lovely quiet street with mature trees, sidewalks and gently sloped streets.', 'Three bedrooms on the main level.', 'Wonderful private backyard with patio.', 'This home is sparkling clean and well maintained.', 'Main Level:', 'Newly finished oak hardwood floors and fresh neutral paint throughout.', 'Three bright bedrooms on the main level have ample closet space.', 'One bedroom also walks through to the kitchen offering flexibility in its use.', 'The bathroom is bright with a ceramic floor and ceramic tub surround.', 'Spacious living room with huge picture window overlooking the front yard.', 'Formal dining area in addition to the “eat-in” kitchen.', 'The kitchen is very functional and offers ceramic tile floors.', 'Lower Level:', 'This level offers a large finished recreation room, good sized laundry room with full-size washer and dryer, utility room, and storage space.', 'Additional Features:', 'Nice and spacious two-and-a-half car garage with electronic door openers.', 'Central air conditioning, new water heater, newer windows throughout, newer roof, and water softener.', 'Approximate Room Sizes:', 'Kitchen:\t13 x 8', 'Living Room: 16 x 11', 'Bedroom 1: 11 x 11', 'Bedroom 2: 11 x 10', 'Bedroom 3: 11 x 9', 'Family Room: 28 x 11', 'Total Finished Square Feet: 1,300', 'St. Louis Park School District #283:', 'No smoking on property', 'Rent: $2,150', 'Deposit: $2,300', 'Application Fee: $50 per adult ($60 for out of state applicants)']
